---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
        title="About - Combda"
        description="Learn about Combda's mission, values, and team. Discover how we deliver expert IT infrastructure and technology solutions."
>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-black">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
            <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 p-8">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-6 tracking-tight"><span class="text-orange-600">admin@combda:~$</span> cat about.txt</h1>

                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-snug">
                        Combda is a premier IT services company dedicated to transforming businesses through
                        innovative technology solutions. We specialize in providing comprehensive IT infrastructure,
                        cloud migration, cybersecurity, and DevOps consulting services.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">OUR MISSION</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-snug">
                        To empower businesses with reliable, scalable, and secure technology solutions that
                        drive growth and operational excellence. We believe in building long-term partnerships
                        with our clients, ensuring their technology infrastructure evolves with their business needs.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">OUR VALUES</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-orange-600 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">├──</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-gray-100 font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">EXCELLENCE:</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-300 leading-snug"> We deliver high-quality solutions that exceed expectations</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-orange-600 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">├──</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-gray-100 font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">INNOVATION:</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-300 leading-snug"> We stay ahead of technology trends to provide cutting-edge solutions</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-orange-600 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">├──</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-gray-100 font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">RELIABILITY:</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-300 leading-snug"> Our clients can count on us for consistent, dependable service</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-orange-600 mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">├──</span>
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-gray-100 font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">PARTNERSHIP:</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-300 leading-snug"> We work collaboratively with our clients as trusted advisors</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">WHY CHOOSE COMBDA?</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-snug">
                        With years of experience in the IT industry, our team brings deep expertise and a
                        proven track record of successful implementations. We understand that every business
                        is unique, which is why we tailor our solutions to meet your specific requirements
                        and budget constraints.
                    </p>

                    <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2 uppercase tracking-tight">READY TO TRANSFORM YOUR IT
                            INFRASTRUCTURE?</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-snug">
                            Let's discuss how Combda can help your business leverage technology for growth and success.
                        </p>
                        <a href="/#contact"
                           class="bg-orange-700 text-black border border-orange-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-none font-medium hover:bg-orange-800 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                            GET IN TOUCH
                            <span class="cursor-blink text-orange-600">█</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>